<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="description" content="The R|C Framework - Relationship-Centric Operating Systems for businesses and organizations.">
    <title>The R|C Framework™</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 0; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; background: #fff; }
        header { background: #1a1a1a; color: white; padding: 5rem 1rem; text-align: center; }
        .container { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 2rem 1rem; }
        h1 { font-size: 2.8rem; margin: 0; }
        h2 { color: #1a1a1a; text-align: center; }
        .cycle { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 1.5rem; justify-content: center; margin: 3rem 0; }
        .step { background: #f8f9fa; padding: 1.8rem; border-radius: 12px; width: 260px; text-align: center; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); }
        form { background: #f8f9fa; padding: 2rem; border-radius: 12px; max-width: 600px; margin: 2rem auto; }
        input, textarea { width: 100%; padding: 12px; margin: 10px 0; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 6px; }
        button { background: #1a1a1a; color: white; padding: 14px 32px; border: none; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 1.1rem; cursor: pointer; }
        .cta { background: #1a1a1a; color: white; padding: 1rem 2rem; border-radius: 6px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>The R|C Framework™</h1>
        <p style="font-size: 1.4rem; max-width: 700px; margin: 1.5rem auto;">Relationship-Centric Operating Systems for Small Businesses and Mission-Driven Organizations</p>
    </header>

    <div class="container">
        <h2>Build Stronger Relationships. Create Sustainable Growth.</h2>
        <p style="text-align: center; font-size: 1.2rem;">The R|C Framework is a practical system that helps organizations move from transactional interactions to deep, productive relationships that drive real ownership and results.</p>

        <h2 style="margin-top: 4rem;">The Framework</h2>
        <div class="cycle">
            <div class="step"><h3>1. Relationship</h3><p>Start with genuine connection and trust.</p></div>
            <div class="step"><h3>2. Connection</h3><p>Deepen engagement and understanding.</p></div>
            <div class="step"><h3>3. Value</h3><p>Deliver consistent, meaningful value.</p></div>
            <div class="step"><h3>4. Invitation</h3><p>Invite deeper participation and co-creation.</p></div>
            <div class="step"><h3>5. Ownership</h3><p>Foster long-term commitment and shared success.</p></div>
        </div>

        <h2>How I Help</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Website & Shopify transformations with relational messaging</li>
            <li>Operations systems and process optimization</li>
            <li>Branding and communication strategy</li>
            <li>AI-enhanced automation that supports human relationships</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 style="margin-top: 3rem;">Work With Me</h2>
        <form action="https://formspree.io/f/your-form-id" method="POST">
            <input type="text" name="name" placeholder="Your Name" required>
            <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Your Email" required>
            <textarea name="message" rows="6" placeholder="Tell me about your project or what you need help with..." required></textarea>
            <button type="submit">Send Message</button>
        </form>

        <p style="text-align: center;">
            Or email me directly: <a href="mailto:elizabeth@thercframework.com">elizabeth@thercframework.com</a>
        </p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
